Name: AuthorizedSourceReference
Description: A reference to the Authorized Source of the value used by this representation. A GeographicStructure may have more than one Authorized Source included in the listing.

Name: GeographicStructureReference
Description: A reference to the GeographicStructure used by this representation.

Name: ExcludedGeographicLevelReference
Description: A reference to a Structure Level that is excluded, not used by, this representation. May be repeated to exclude multiple Structure values.
